data.text: Make your ultimate bedroom retreat a reality with a one-of-a-kind custom upholstered bed. Our nearly limitless designer options mean you can personalize every detail to create your signature look. Once you’ve chosen your headboard style, select your favorite fabric or leather cover. Define your bed size and choose from four headboard height choices. Then, select a leg style and add an optional molding or nail trim (on select models) if desired. Finish the exposed wood elements of your custom creation with any shade from our standard stain and paint options, metallics, MIY paints, and artisanal finishes. Personalize your upholstered bed and headboard and make it yours.
